snippet.title: Nocturnal - Launch Trailer (PC, PS5, Xbox, Switch)
snippet.description:
We are happy to announce that Nocturnal is available now on PC, PS5, Xbox Series & Nintendo Switch!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1634080/Nocturnal/
PS5: https://store.playstation.com/fr-fr/concept/10006038
Xbox Series:https://www.xbox.com/en-us/games/store/nocturnal/9nj87v9twkgl
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/nocturnal-switch/

More about our games on:
http://sunnysidegames.ch
